Title: API: fixing the password behaviour where no activate change states were previously registered
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: core
Date: 1612798519
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0b7

In the previous version, when creating, editing or deleting a password
via the API, the change was not registered as a pending change state. This
werk fixes this behaviour. Furthermore, it also fixes the behaviour 
of the delete endpoint.
